INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2017-05-02 16:19:28','2017-05-02 16:19:28','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2017-05-02 16:19:28','2017-05-02 16:19:28','',0,'http:/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2017-05-02 16:19:28','2017-05-02 16:19:28','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http:///wp/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2017-05-02 16:19:28','2017-05-02 16:19:28','',0,'http:/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2017-05-02 16:21:37','2017-05-02 21:21:37','\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/conference-button-VOLUNTEER--285x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Volunticipate</a></h3>		\n			<p><strong>Program Team / Advisory Team / Day-of Choices / Other</strong></p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/Home-Page-conference-button-register--300x297.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Conference 2017</a></h3>		\n			<p><strong>Session Proposal Form / Conference Info &amp; Schedule / Camp Limmud</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Shabbat: the REST of Limmud</strong></p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/conference-button-SUPPORT-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Support</a></h3>		\n			<p><strong>Donate / Friends of LimmudBoston / Advertise / Exhibit / Silent Auction</strong></p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/conference-button-SUPPORT-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">About  Us</a></h3>		\n			<p><strong> About U</strong>s </p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/feet-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h4><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Presenter Name</a></h4>		\n			<p>This great person will share her brilliance on ...</p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/Sharon-and-Rich-Solomon-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h4><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Brilliant Presenter #2</a></h4>		\n			<p>This session is just great. The presenter is smart.</p>\n			<h3>Testimonials</h3>\n			<p>LimmudBoston was the most inspiring I have ever attended!<em> <br /></em></p><p><em>A lively, perky presento. Good discussion about a difficult abstract topic - done well.</em></p><p><em>Well organized, lots of info, passionate speakers. Great links between audio / video - the press conference etc... Clearly a labor of love by the presenter.</em></p><p> </p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"> </p>		\n			<p><em>Great mix of text study and Philosophy and great ending with an article. Great at including participants. Great job!</em></p><p>Really interesting, presented in an easy to follow and understandable manner, accessible to all levels of Jewish knowledge!</p><p><em>Personal, small, educations, fun, very thought provoking.  Very knowledgeable presenter!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"> </p>		\n			<p>Very informative and engaging. I learned new ways of looking at known text.</p><p><em>Made me think differently about the topic and what it means in life.  Also \'bag of connotations\" more broadly - great! Even with my rudimentary Hebrew, I could follow.</em></p><p>Drew attendees into intense discussion, both philosophical and personal. Also helped me re-intererpret familiar passages from the tradition in new ways. Jeremy was very open to discussion and good at leading it.</p><p><em><style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></style>Excellent presentation. Having us write evoked many memories. I learned a lot and have much more information about poetry.</em></p>		\n		<h3>Session Proposals Due By October 2</h3>\n		<p>Session proposal form arrives by email with registration confirmation. REGISTER HERE</p>\n			<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Register Here!\n					</a>\n<h3>\n		About Us\n	</h3>\n	<p>LimmudBoston is a happening, a Jewish learningfest of culture and identity. From storytelling, music and meditation to Torah and Talmud, LimmudBoston offers inspiration and education – engaging beginners and scholars alike.</p>\n<p>Address: PO Box 36, Waban, MA 02468</p>\n<p>Phone: 1-617-299-15200</p>\n<p>Email: info@LimmudBoston.org</p>\n<h3>\n		Our Services\n	</h3>\n	<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec feugiat ultricies vulputate. Suspendisse quis lacinia erat, eu tincidunt ante. Pellentesque aliquet feugiat tellus, et feugiat to