=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2015/camp-limmud/\">More…</a>\r\n<h4><a title=\"Teens at LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/teens-at-limmudboston/\">Teens</a></h4>\r\nGroups of teens as well as individuals are welcome at LimmudBoston!  <a title=\"Teens at LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/teens-at-limmudboston/\">More…</a>\r\n<h4><a title=\"CJP Educators\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2015/educators/\">CJP Educators</a></h4>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>','Conference 2017','','publish','closed','closed','','conference-2017','','','2017-05-30 18:24:51','2017-05-30 23:24:51','',0,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/?page_id=80',0,'page','',0),(81,3,'2017-05-26 12:12:17','2017-05-26 17:12:17','<h1>Conference 2017</h1>\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\nThe 2017 conference will take place Sunday, December 3 at Temple Reyim, 1860 Washington Street, Newton. <em>Shabbat: the REST of Limmud on Dec. 1 &amp; 2.</em>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Ticket Prices</h3>\r\nEarlybird adult registration: $45\r\n\r\nCamp Limmud (ages 3-13): $25\r\n\r\nYoung Adults who sign up to volunteer: $25\r\n\r\nPlease contact Steffi at <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> in case of financial hardship. (No one is turned away.)\r\n\r\nClick here to register and get tickets\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Special Programs at LimmudBoston</h3>\r\n<h4><a title=\"Camp Limmud\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2017/conference-2015/camp-limmud/\">Camp Limmud</a></h4>\r\nRegistration closes Monday, November 27 for the Camp Limmud programming for children ages 3-13.   <a title=\"Camp Limmud\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2015/camp-limmud/\">More…</a>\r\n<h4><a title=\"Teens at LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/teens-at-limmudboston/\">Teens</a></h4>\r\nGroups of teens as well as individuals are welcome at LimmudBoston!  <a title=\"Teens at LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/t