ads/2014/03/chapel_presenting-200x300.jpg 200w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/chapel_presenting-100x150.jpg 100w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/chapel_presenting.jpg 533w\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">© Meri Bond</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Please read carefully: Start by registering for the conference.\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nHelp us offer a creative, dynamic, enticing conference for the entire Jewish community!\r\n\r\nIn keeping with Limmud International Values and Principles,  everyone is a learner at LimmudBoston. Presenters are also attendees. <strong>Register for LimmudBoston in order to receive the link to our Presenter Submission Form</strong>. If your session is accepted, please plan on attending the conference for the day in addition to your session. The presenter form link comes with conference registration materials.\r\n\r\nWe welcome sessions on all Jewish topics, at many levels and in diverse media. Offer your passion: conventional or un-. Hands-on programs are especially welcome.\r\n\r\nMultiple submissions are welcome. Kindly complete one form for each session submitted. Please note that the Program Team might choose only one, as we try to include as many presenters as possible.\r\n\r\nConsider, too, offering a session for any of our three Camp Limmud programs, ages 3-5, 6-8 or 9-13.\r\n\r\n<em>If event registration fee is a hardship, write to <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> to discuss a registration adjustment.</em>\r\n\r\nPresenters will be notified on a rolling basis, starting mid-August.\r\n\r\n<strong>Click for conference registration <a href=\"https://limmudboston2017.eventbrite.com\">HERE</a>.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>','Presenter Info','','inherit','closed','closed','','30-revision-v1','','','2017-05-26 12:15:40','2017-05-26 17:15:40','',30,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/30-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(85,3,'2017