apper\"></div>\r\nYour LimmudBoston donation goes to the creation of LimmudBoston programs and planning. Yes, we are a Massachusetts 501(c)3 corporation. As a volunteer-run organization, nearly 100 percent of your donation is directly applied to LimmudBoston programming. We currently seek funds for scholarships and invited guests.\r\n\r\nWe’re growing. With your financial assistance, we can continue to inspire and educate with the sensational LimmudBoston 2014 program, including more presenters from out-of-town, an expanded Camp Limmud, LimmudBoston Shabbat, the LimmudBoston Fellows Program and more.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/make-a-donation/\">CLICK HERE TO DONATE ONLINE OR BY CHECK</a>\r\n<h3>Friends of LimmudBoston</h3>\r\nBecome an organizational Friend of LimmudBoston by choosing the appropriate donation <a class=\"external\" href=\"http://lb2016.eventbrite.com\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Prophets</strong>, $360 and above, includes 4 tickets to LimmudBoston 2014, as well as both Program Book and online listing\r\n\r\n<strong>Scholars</strong>, $180-$359, includes 2 tickets to LimmudBoston 2014, as well as both Program Book and online listing\r\n\r\n<strong>Learners</strong>, $118-$179, includes both Program Book and online listing\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Become a Friend of LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/\">More…</a>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n<div id=\"sidebar\">\r\n<div id=\"text-4\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Become a Friend of LimmudBoston</h3>\r\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\r\n\r\nA wonderful way to support our work is to become a Friend of LimmudBoston. <a href=\"https://www.limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/\">Find out more here</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"text-5\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\r\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/support/friends-of-limmudboston-2016/\"> 2016 Friends of LimmudBoston</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/support/2015-friends-of-limmudboston\">2015 Friends of LimmudBoston</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/support/2014-friends-of-limmudboston\">2014 Friends of LimmudBoston</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Support','','inherit','closed','closed','','92-revision-v1','','','2017-05-26 12:29:03','2017-05-26 17:29:03','',92,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/92-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(96,3,'2017-05-26 12:30:50','2017-05-26 17:30:50','<div id=\"header_container\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"content_container\" class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"eight columns\">\r\n<div id=\"middle-col\">Make a Donation\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2718 size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/limmud-boston-program-book640.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcset=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/limmud-boston-program-book640.jpg 640w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/limmud-boston-program-book640-150x69.jpg 150w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/limmud-boston-program-book640-300x138.jpg 300w\" alt=\"LimmudBoston Program Book 2015\" width=\"640\" height=\"295\" />\r\n\r\nPlease click on this Donate button:\r\n\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n</form>Your LimmudBoston donation helps us continue the work which inspires and unites New England’s many Jewish communities. Your donation also helps us continue the core practice of Limmud International, that all who wish to learn can be included, regardless of financial circumstances.\r\n\r\nLimmudBoston, Inc. is a 501(c)3 tax exempt organization. Contributions are tax deductible to the extent allowed by law as long as LimmudBoston, Inc. provided no goods or services in exchange for your contribution.\r\n\r\nDonations received before November 15 will be acknowledged in the annual LimmudBoston conference program book given to every conference attendee.\r\n\r\nPlease consider the following amounts, or choose an amount that fits your wallet:\r\n\r\n<strong>Pillars of Learning</strong>, $500 or more, may sponsor a presenter and receive 4 admissions;\r\n\r\n<strong>Prophets</strong>, $360-499, receive conference admission for four;\r\n\r\n<strong>Scholars</strong>, $180-359, receive conference admission for two;\r\n\r\n<strong>Learners</strong>, $118-179, receive conference admission for one;\r\n\r\n<strong>Well-Wishers</strong>, $72 &amp; above, will be listed in the LimmudBoston Program Book.\r\n\r\nHere is another opportunity to click on the DONATE button:\r\n\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n</form>If you prefer, you can send a check by mail. Please make your check payable to LimmudBoston with “LimmudBoston” in the memo line, and send it to:\r\n\r\nLimmudBoston\r\nPO Box 36\r\nWaban MA 02468\r\n\r\nNotes\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Your contribution will be noted in the LimmudBoston Program Book.</li>\r\n 	<li>Please indicate if you wish to remain anonymous.</li>\r\n 	<li>If you wish to make a donation in honor of, or in memory of, one or more people, please indicate this and the information will be included.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sponsorship opportunities are available. For details contact LimmudBoston  <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org </a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n<div id=\"sidebar\">\r\n<div id=\"text-4\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Become a Friend of LimmudBoston</h3>\r\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\r\n\r\nA wonderful way to support our work is to become a Friend of LimmudBoston. <a href=\"https://www.limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/\">Find out more here</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"text-5\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\r\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/make-a-donation/support/friends-of-limmudboston-2016/\"> 2016 Friends of LimmudBoston</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/make-a-donation/support/2015-friends-of-limmudboston\">2015 Friends of LimmudBoston</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/make-a-donation/support/2014-friends-of-limmudboston\">2014 Friends of LimmudBoston</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/make-a-donation/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Make a Donation','','inherit','closed','closed','','38-revision-v1','','','2017-05-26 12:30:50','2017-05-26 17:30:50','',38,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/38-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(97,3,'2017-05-26 12:33:13','2017-05-26 17:33:13','<div id=\"content_container\" class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"eight columns\">\r\n<div id=\"middle-col\">\r\n<h1>Become a Friend of LimmudBoston</h1>\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n\r\nGo to the <a href=\"https://limmudboston2017.eventbrite.com\">Registration Form</a> and choose the appropriate donation type to become an organizational Friend of LimmudBoston.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://lb2016.eventbrite.com/\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Friends of LimmudBoston Logo\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Friends_logo.jpg\" alt=\"Friends of LimmudBoston Logo\" width=\"432\" height=\"225\" /></a>\r\n<h2>Benefits for Friends of LimmudBoston:</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>LimmudBoston links to your website.</li>\r\n 	<li>Your organization is mentioned in LimmudBoston program book and literature.</li>\r\n 	<li>You are recognized as part of the LimmudBoston community.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you have questions about becoming a Friend of LimmudBoston, write to <a href=\"mailto:info@limmudboston.org\">info@limmudboston.org</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nOrganizational support helps LimmudBoston continue to provide educational programs that stimulate and engage learners of all ages. We are pleased to provide the following benefits to our Friends for their generous contributions.\r\n<h3>Pillars $500 and above</h3>\r\nAn organizational contribution at this level includes four (4) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\r\n<h3>Prophets $360 and above</h3>\r\nAn organizational contribution at this level includes four (4) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\r\n<h3>Scholars $180 – $359</h3>\r\nAn organizational contribution at this level provides two (2) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\r\n<h3>Learners $118 – $179</h3>\r\nAn organizational contribution at this level provides a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\r\n<h3>Well-wishers $72 – $117</h3>\r\n<h2>Friends of LimmudBoston have just a few responsibilities:</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Link to the LimmudBoston website — in exchange for our linking to your website.</li>\r\n 	<li>Designate a key contact for LimmudBoston communication.</li>\r\n 	<li>Recruit volunticipants from your organization to join LimmudBoston committees (at least one, possibly more).</li>\r\n 	<li>Promote LimmudBoston in your newsletters and communications.</li>\r\n 	<li>Support LimmudBoston financially.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nFeel free to email <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> with any questions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFriends of Limmud, please add the banner at the top of this page to your website. You can download it by clicking <a title=\"\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Friends_logo.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-0\" data-imagelightbox=\"0\">here.</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"four columns\">\r\n<div id=\"sidebar\">\r\n<div id=\"text-5\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\r\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Friends of LimmudBoston','','inherit','closed','closed','','49-revision-v1','','','2017-05-26 12:33:13','2017-05-26 17:33:13','',49,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/49-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(98,3,'2017-05-26 12:34:22','2017-05-26 17:34:22','<div id=\"content_container\" class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"nine columns\">\r\n<div id=\"right-col\">\r\n<h1>Advertise</h1>\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n<h4><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-581\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/open_program_book.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" srcset=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/open_program_book.jpg 250w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/open_program_book-150x99.jpg 150w\" alt=\"open_program_book\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" /></h4>\r\nAdvertise in the very guide which every LimmudBoston participant will hold all day long, and save for years to come.  Please provide a black &amp; white JPG or PDF of your ad.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://ads-exhibits-auction.eventbrite.com\">RESERVE ADVERTISING</a>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Ad Rates</h3>\r\nFull page:  8in w x 10in h – $359  –  Half page:  8in w x 5in h – $235  –  Quarter page:  4in w x 5in h – $119\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<em>Camera-ready, black-and-white</em> artwork in the form of a PDF or JPG must be received at <a href=\"mailto:info@limmudboston.org?Subject=Advertising\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> no later than Friday, November 10.  Write  “Advertising” in the subject line.\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one column\"></div>\r\n</div>','Advertisers','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2017-05-26 12:34:22','2017-05-26 17:34:22','',42,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/42-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(99,3,'2017-05-26 12:38:57','2017-05-26 17:38:57','<div class=\"crumbs\"><a class=\"crumb\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2017/\">Conference 2017</a></div>\r\n<h1>Exhibit</h1>\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n<h2>Exhibitors are welcome at LimmudBoston</h2>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_1849\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a title=\"\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IsraelExhibitor.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-0\" data-imagelightbox=\"0\"><img class=\"wp-image-1849 size-medium\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IsraelExhibitor-300x200.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IsraelExhibitor-300x200.jpg 300w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IsraelExhibitor-150x100.jpg 150w, https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IsraelExhibitor.jpg 800w\" alt=\"2014 Exhibitor table\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">©Meri Bond</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a href=\"https://ads-exhibits-auction.eventbrite.com\">EXHIBITOR RESERVATION</a>\r\n<del></del>\r\n<h4 class=\"clear\">Pricing</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>One for-profit table: $250; One non-profit table: $150</li>\r\n 	<li>Half of a table (artists only): $100</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe LimmudBoston Exhibitor Team aims for a balance of companies displaying products for purchase with non-profit organizations.\r\n<h4>Note to reserved table holders:</h4>\r\nA table is not guaranteed until a <a title=\"Exhibitor Contract – Terms and Conditions\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2014/exhibit/exhibitor-contract/\">signed contract</a> with payment is received and LimmudBoston has sent a letter of confirmation.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://ads-exhibits-auction.eventbrite.com\"><strong>REGISTER EXHIBITOR</strong></a>\r\n\r\nWith prior coordination with LimmudBoston planners, exhibitors may offer sessions at their booth. Propose sessions on exhibitor registration form.  (LINK NEEDED HERE) The LimmudBoston Program Team must accept session proposals.  For details contact <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org </a>\r\n<h4>Remember:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Exhibitors agree to present for the entire day of conference, from 8am – 6pm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Exhibitor tables include one admission ticket to LimmudBoston. If absolutely necessary, you may invite one additional table attendant. For security purposes, names of anyone entering the building must be submitted in advance of conference.</li>\r\n 	<li>Read and complete the <a title=\"Exhibitor Contract – Terms and Conditions\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2014/exhibit/exhibitor-contract/\">Exhibitor Contract</a>. <a href=\"https:/