oston.org/conference-2017/conference-2015/camp-limmud/\">Camp Limmud</a></h4>\r\nRegistration closes Monday, November 27 for the Camp Limmud programming for children ages 3-13.   <a title=\"Camp Limmud\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2015/camp-limmud/\">More…</a>\r\n<h4><a title=\"Teens at LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/teens-at-limmudboston/\">Teens</a></h4>\r\nGroups of teens as well as individuals are welcome at LimmudBoston!  <a title=\"Teens at LimmudBoston\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/teens-at-limmudboston/\">More…</a>\r\n<h4><a title=\"CJP Educators\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2015/educators/\">CJP Educators</a></h4>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>','Conference 2017','','inherit','closed','closed','','80-revision-v1','','','2017-05-30 18:24:51','2017-05-30 23:24:51','',80,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/80-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(188,3,'2017-05-30 18:25:56','2017-05-30 23:25:56','<h1>48in48: This page needs corrections!</h1>\r\na) This page belongs under \"Past Conferences\"\r\n\r\nb) The link to each person\'s video should connect to their photograph, but they do not. Please talk to me about repairing this page.CORRECT LINKS ARE ON THIS PAGE, below the photos: https://limmudboston.org/chai-alive-video-2015/\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<h1>Chai Alive! Video Project</h1>\r\n<div class=\"post-entry\">\r\n\r\nChai Alive! videos captured personal Jewish memories from 20 LimmudBoston 2015 participants. Ken Hausman of <a href=\"http://www.hhhvideo.com/About_HHH_Video.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HHH Video</a> specializes in helping families create personalized legacy videos to keep for generations to come. Family members interview parents and grandparents, cousins and others to preserve family stories and histories for future generations.\r\n\r\nWe thank these LimmudBoston participants for sharing their stories. Click on a name (below these photographs) to watch. Chai Alive! videos will return for LimmudBoston 2016! What story will YOU tell?\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id=\"gallery-1\" class=\"gallery galleryid-2621 gallery-columns-5 gallery-size-full\">\r\n<dl class=\"gallery-item\">\r\n 	<dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Aaron-Seidman.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd id=\"gallery-1-2761\" class=\"wp-caption-text gallery-caption\">Aaron Seidman</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"gallery-item\">\r\n 	<dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Avi-Wald.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd id=\"gallery-1-2762\" class=\"wp-caption-text gallery-caption\">Avi W.</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"gallery-item\">\r\n 	<dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Bruce-Levy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd id=\"gallery-1-2763\" class=\"wp-caption-text gallery-caption\">Bruce Levy</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"gallery-item\">\r\n 	<dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Cindy-Rifka-Marshal.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd id=\"gallery-1-2764\" class=\"wp-caption-text gallery-caption\">Cindy Rivka Marshall</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"gallery-item\">\r\n 	<dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Dan-Karp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></dt>\r\n 	<dd id=\"gallery-1-2765\" class=\"wp-caption-text gallery-caption\">Dan Karp</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"gallery-item\">\r\n 	<dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org