 great ending with an article. Great at including participants. Great job!</em></p><p>Really interesting, presented in an easy to follow and understandable manner, accessible to all levels of Jewish knowledge!</p><p><em>Personal, small, educations, fun, very thought provoking.  Very knowledgeable presenter!</em></p>		\n			<p>Very informative and engaging. I learned new ways of looking at known text.</p><p><em>Made me think differently about the topic and what it means in life.  Also \'bag of connotations\" more broadly - great! Even with my rudimentary Hebrew, I could follow.</em></p><p>Drew attendees into intense discussion, both philosophical and personal. Also helped me re-intererpret familiar passages from the tradition in new ways. Jeremy was very open to discussion and good at leading it.</p><p><em><style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></style>Excellent presentation. Having us write evoked many memories. I learned a lot and have much more information about poetry.</em></p>		\n		<h3>Join Us Now!</h3>\n		<p>Join Us to stay up to date and volunteer with <strong>LimmudBoston</strong>.</p>\n			<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/about/contact-us/\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Join Us\n					</a>\n<h3>\n		Our Services\n	</h3>\n	<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec feugiat ultricies vulputate. Suspendisse quis lacinia erat, eu tincidunt ante. Pellentesque aliquet feugiat tellus, et feugiat tortor porttitor vel. Nullam id scelerisque magna. Curabitur placerat sodales placerat. Nunc dignissim ac velit vel lobortis.</p>\n<h3>\n		Find Us\n	</h3>\n	<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyD09zQ9PNDNNy9TadMuzRV_UsPUoWKntt8&q=Temple+Reyim%2C+1860+Washington+St.%2C+Auburndale%2C+MA+02466\" style=\"border:0;width:100%;height:300px\"></iframe>\n<h3>\n		Contact Us\n	</h3>\n','Front page1','','inherit','closed','closed','','240-revision-v1','','','2017-06-03