s another opportunity to click on the DONATE button:</p>\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" type=\"image\" /></p>\n</form>\n<p>If you prefer, you can send a check by mail. Please make your check payable to LimmudBoston with “LimmudBoston” in the memo line, and send it to:</p>\n<p>LimmudBoston<br />\nPO Box 36<br />\nWaban MA 02468</p>\n<p>Notes</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Your contribution will be noted in the LimmudBoston Program Book.</li>\n<li>Please indicate if you wish to remain anonymous.</li>\n<li>If you wish to make a donation in honor of, or in memory of, one or more people, please indicate this and the information will be included.</li>\n<li>Sponsorship opportunities are available. For details contact LimmudBoston  <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org </a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n	<h3>Become a Friend of LimmudBoston</h3>\n<p>A wonderful way to support our work is to become a Friend of LimmudBoston. <a href=\"https://www.limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/\">Find out more here</a>.</p>\n<h3>Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/silent-auction/support/friends-of-limmudboston-2016/\"> 2016 Friends of LimmudBoston</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/silent-auction/support/2015-friends-of-limmudboston\">2015 Friends of LimmudBoston</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/silent-auction/support/2014-friends-of-limmudboston\">2014 Friends of LimmudBoston</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/silent-auction/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a></p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/conference-button-SUPPORT-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" itempr