rder:0;width:100%;height:200px\"></iframe>\n<h3>Register to propose your session for December 3, 2017</h3>\n<p><strong>May 30: 8pm-4:15am</strong> Community Tikkun Leil Shavuot, Cong. KI in Brookline<strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p><strong>June 2: 8:30-10:am </strong>Advisory Team meeting at Temple Reyim, 1860 Washington St., Newton</p>\n			<a href=\"https://limmudboston2017.eventbrite.com/\" target=\"_self\" role=\"button\">\n							Register Now\n					</a>\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">About Us</h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">LimmudBoston is a happening, a Jewish learningfest of culture and identity. From storytelling, music and meditation to Torah and Talmud, LimmudBoston offers inspiration and education – engaging beginners and scholars alike.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/who-we-are\">Learn more &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Social Media</h4>\n	<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact Us</h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><small><small><a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/about/contact-us\">Join our mailing list</a> to stay up to date and volunteer with LimmudBoston.</small></small></p>\n','Front Page 2','','inherit','closed','closed','','326-revision-v1','','','2017-06-03 15:45:16','2017-06-03 20:45:16','',326,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/326-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(363,1,'2017-06-03 15:54:34','2017-06-03 20:54:34','{\n    \"custom_css[bb-theme]\": {\n        \"value\": \"/*\\nYou can add your own CSS here.\\n\\nClick the help icon above to learn more.\\n*/\\n/* 6 circles*/\\n.featured-circles {\\nheight: 100px;\\nwidth: 100px;\\nborder-radius: 50%;\\ntext-align: center;\\nline-height: 100px;\\n}\\n.text-circle {\\nbackground-color  : #A4278D !important;\\n}\\n.Israel-circle {\\nbackground-color  : #F37023 !important;\\n}\\n.family-circle {\\nbackground-color  : #28A9E1 !important;\\n}\\n.spirituality-circle {\\nbackground-color  : #C1D730 !important;\