<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/feet-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h4><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Presenter Name</a></h4>		\n			<p>This great person will share her brilliance on ...</p>\n				<a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\" itemprop=\"url\">\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/Sharon-and-Rich-Solomon-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" itemprop=\"image\"  />\n				</a>\n	<h4><a href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Brilliant Presenter #2</a></h4>		\n			<p>This session is just great. The presenter is smart.</p>\n			<h3>Testimonials</h3>\n			<p>LimmudBoston was the most inspiring I have ever attended!<em> <br /></em></p><p><em>A lively, perky presento. Good discussion about a difficult abstract topic - done well.</em></p><p><em>Well organized, lots of info, passionate speakers. Great links between audio / video - the press conference etc... Clearly a labor of love by the presenter.</em></p><p> </p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"> </p>		\n			<p><em>Great mix of text study and Philosophy and great ending with an article. Great at including participants. Great job!</em></p><p>Really interesting, presented in an easy to follow and understandable manner, accessible to all levels of Jewish knowledge!</p><p><em>Personal, small, educations, fun, very thought provoking.  Very knowledgeable presenter!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"> </p>		\n			<p>Very informative and engaging. I learned new ways of looking at known text.</p><p><em>Made me think differently about the topic and what it means in life.  Also \'bag of connotations\" more broadly - great! Even with my rudimentary Hebrew, I could follow.</em></p><p>Drew attendees into intense discussion, both philosophical and personal. Also helped me re-intererpret familiar passages from the tradition in new ways. Jeremy was very open to discussion and good at leading it.</p><p><em><style type=\"text/css