'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/268-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(371,4,'2017-06-03 16:08:58','2017-06-03 21:08:58','\n				<img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/conference-button-VOLUNTEER--285x300.jpg\" alt=\"conference button VOLUNTEER\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"300\" width=\"285\"  />\n	<h1>Volunticipate!</h1>\n	<h4>Volunteer + Participate = Volunticipate!</h4>\n	<p>We can’t do this without you!</p>\n<p>Volunteering is a core value at Limmuds throughout the world. Presenter to name tag collector, setup to cleanup, Limmud participants pay to attend, and also volunteer in order to help support their local Limmud conference.  Please join a volunteer team, or choose a volunteer task, so that we can keep LimmudBoston affordable and accessible to all.</p>\n	<p>To join a planning team: (Link to SFDC)</p>\n<p>Click HERE to choose a task for LimmudBoston conference on Sunday, December 3, or on setup days (November 30, December 1).</p>\n','Volunticipate!','','inherit','closed','closed','','21-revision-v1','','','2017-06-03 16:08:58','2017-06-03 21:08:58','',21,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/21-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(372,6,'2017-06-03 16:14:05','2017-06-03 21:14:05','','162_MBond_161204_4650-ws','','inherit','open','closed','','162_mbond_161204_4650-ws','','','2017-06-03 16:14:05','2017-06-03 21:14:05','',44,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/wp/../sites/limmudboston/uploads/2017/05/162_MBond_161204_4650-ws.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(373,6,'2017-06-03 16:14:07','2017-06-03 21:14:07','','163_MBond_161204_4658-ws','','inherit','open','closed','','163_mbond_161204_4658-ws','','','2017-06-03 16:14:07','2017-06-03 21:14:07','',44,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/wp/../sites/limmudboston/uploads/2017/05/163_MBond_161204_4658-ws.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(374,6,'2017-06-03 16:15:53','2017-06-03 21:15:53','\n	<h1>Exhibitors are welcome at LimmudBoston</h1>\n<p><img src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/163_MBond_161204_4658-ws-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></p>\n<h3>Pricing as below:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">One for-profit table: $250;</li>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">One non-profit table: $150</li>\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Half of a table (artists only): $100</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The LimmudBoston Exhibitor Team aims for a balance of companies displaying products for purchase with non-profit organizations.</p>\n<h4><strong>Note to reserved table holders:</strong></h4>\n<p>A table is not guaranteed until a <a title=\"Exhibitor Contract – Terms and Conditions\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2014/exhibit/exhibitor-contract/\">signed contract</a> with payment is received and LimmudBoston has sent a letter of confirmation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ads-exhibits-auction.eventbrite.com\"><strong>REGISTER EXHIBITOR</strong></a></p>\n<p>With prior coordination with LimmudBoston planners, exhibitors may offer sessions at their booth. Propose sessions on exhibitor registration form.  (LINK NEEDED HERE) The LimmudBoston Program Team must accept session proposals.  For details contact <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org </a></p>\n<h4>Remember:</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Exhibitors agree to present for the entire day of conference, from 8am – 6pm.</li>\n<li>Exhibitor tables include one admission ticket to LimmudBoston. If absolutely necessary, you may invite one additional table attendant. For security purposes, names of anyone entering the building must be submitted in advance of conference.</li>\n<li>Read and complete the <a title=\"Exhibitor Contract – Terms and Conditions\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/conference-2014/exhibit/exhibitor-contract/\">Exhibitor Contract</a>. <a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/2016-Exhibitor-Contract.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Click here</a> to download a printable copy of the Exhibitor Contract.</li>\n<li>Print the completed contract and mail it, with payment, to:<br />\nLimmudBoston, PO Box 36, Waban, MA 02468</li>\n<li>Some exhibitors like to share. However, one exhibitor must accept responsibility for the entire table. Write <a href=\"mailto:info@limmudboston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> with “Exhibitors” in the subject line if you want to share.  No guarantees! We will try to find another exhibitor to share with you.</li>\n</ol>\n','Exhibitors','','inherit','closed','closed','','44-revision-v1','','','2017-06-03 16:15:53','2017-06-03 21:15:53','',44,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/44-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(375,4,'2017-06-03 16:26:42','2017-06-03 21:26:42','\n	<h1>Volunticipate!</h1>\n	<h4>Volunteer + Participate = Volunticipate!</h4>\n	<p>We can’t do this without you!</p>\n<p>Volunteering is a core value at Limmuds throughout the world. Presenter to name tag collector, setup to cleanup, Limmud participants pay to attend, and also volunteer in order to help support their local Limmud conference.  Please join a volunteer team, or choose a volunteer task, so that we can keep LimmudBoston affordable and accessible to all.</p>\n	<p>To join a planning team: (Link to SFDC)</p>\n<p>Click HERE to choose a task for LimmudBoston conference on Sunday, December 3, or on setup days (November 30, December 1).</p>\n','Volunticipate!','','inherit','closed','closed','','21-revision-v1','','','2017-06-03 16:26:42','2017-06-03 21:26:42','',21,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/21-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(376,6,'2017-06-03 16:55:45','2017-06-03 21:55:45','\n	Become a Friend of LimmudBoston\n<p>Go to the <a href=\"https://limmudboston2017.eventbrite.com\">Registration Form</a> and choose the appropriate donation type to become an organizational Friend of LimmudBoston.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://lb2016.eventbrite.com/\"><img title=\"Friends of LimmudBoston Logo\" src=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Friends_logo.jpg\" alt=\"Friends of LimmudBoston Logo\" width=\"432\" height=\"225\" /></a></p>\n<h2>Benefits for Friends of LimmudBoston:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>LimmudBoston links to your website.</li>\n<li>Your organization is mentioned in LimmudBoston program book and literature.</li>\n<li>You are recognized as part of the LimmudBoston community.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have questions about becoming a Friend of LimmudBoston, write to <a href=\"mailto:info@limmudboston.org\">info@limmudboston.org</a></p>\n<p>Organizational support helps LimmudBoston continue to provide educational programs that stimulate and engage learners of all ages. We are pleased to provide the following benefits to our Friends for their generous contributions.</p>\n<h3>Pillars $500 and above</h3>\n<p>An organizational contribution at this level includes four (4) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.</p>\n<h3>Prophets $360 and above</h3>\n<p>An organizational contribution at this level includes four (4) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.</p>\n<h3>Scholars $180 – $359</h3>\n<p>An organizational contribution at this level provides two (2) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.</p>\n<h3>Learners $118 – $179</h3>\n<p>An organizational contribution at this level provides a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.</p>\n<h3>Well-wishers $72 – $117</h3>\n<h2>Friends of LimmudBoston have just a few responsibilities:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Link to the LimmudBoston website — in exchange for our linking to your website.</li>\n<li>Designate a key contact for LimmudBoston communication.</li>\n<li>Recruit volunticipants from your organization to join LimmudBoston committees (at least one, possibly more).</li>\n<li>Promote LimmudBoston in your newsletters and communications.</li>\n<li>Support LimmudBoston financially.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Feel free to email <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> with any questions.</p>\n<p>Please add the banner at the top of this page to your website. You can download it by clicking <a title=\"\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Friends_logo.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-0\" data-imagelightbox=\"0\">here.</a></p>\n<h3>Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a></p>\n','Friends of LimmudBoston','','inherit','closed','closed','','49-revision-v1','','','2017-06-03 16:55:45','2017-06-03 21:55:45','',49,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/49-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(377,4,'2017-06-03 16:56:17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\n    \"nav_menu_item[-9028937742727315000]\": {\n        \"value\": false,\n        \"type\": \"nav_menu_item\",\n        \"user_id\": 4\n    }\n}','','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','f539df23-997f-4e5d-8647-39e6b0b7f853','','','2017-06-03 16:56:17','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/?p=377',0,'customize_changeset','',0),(378,4,'2017-06-03 16:59:42','2017-06-03 21:59:42','','Above-Footer','','publish','closed','closed','','above-footer','','','2017-06-03 16:59:42','2017-06-03 21:59:42','',0,'http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/fl-builder-template/above-footer',0,'fl-builder-template','',0),(379,6,'2017-06-03 17:13:23','2017-06-03 22:13:23','\n	<h1style=\"text-align: left;\">Advertise</h1>\n<p>Advertise in the very guide which every LimmudBoston participant will hold all day long, and save for years to come.  Please provide a black &amp; white JPG or PDF of your ad.</p>\n<p>